# üìà Stock Viewer

A simple web app to view live and historical stock prices for popular companies like AAPL, MSFT, GOOGL, and more.

## üöÄ Live Demo
üîó [View the App](https://stock-view-api.vercel.app)

## üí° Features
- Fetches real-time stock data via a Django API
- Beautiful line charts for each stock using Recharts
- Responsive design with Tailwind CSS
- Clean and intuitive UI
- Backend hosted on Render, Frontend on Vercel

## ‚öôÔ∏è Tech Stack

### Frontend
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- Recharts
- Axios
- Vercel (hosting)

### Backend
- Django + Django REST Framework
- yFinance (for stock data)
- Render (hosting)
- CORS Headers for cross-origin requests

## üõ†Ô∏è Setup Instructions

### Backend (Django)

1. Clone the repo:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/istimons/stock-viewer.git
   cd stock-viewer
   ```

2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```

3. Run the server:
   ```bash
   python manage.py runserver
   ```

### Frontend (React)

1. Navigate to the frontend folder:
   ```bash
   cd frontend
   ```

2. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```

3. Run the app:
   ```bash
   npm start
   ```

## üì¶ Deployment

- **Backend:** Deployed to [Render](https://render.com)
- **Frontend:** Deployed to [Vercel](https://vercel.com)

## üìß Contact

Have feedback or suggestions? Reach out at [istimons@gmail.com].


